                Revised 4-Week Development Plan

## Week 1 – Real-Time PPE Detection

### Objective
Build the core AI-powered PPE detection pipeline.

### Tasks
- Set up live video input using OpenCV (webcam/CCTV/video).
- Train and optimize the YOLOv8 PPE detection model.
- Detect workers, safety helmets, and safety vests in real time.
- Display bounding boxes and confidence scores.
- Implement basic PPE violation detection (missing helmet and missing vest).

### Deliverable
A working real-time PPE detection system that processes live video and identifies workers, helmets, and safety vests.

---

## Week 2 – AI & Backend Integration

### Objective
Integrate the YOLO detection pipeline with the FastAPI backend.

### Tasks
- Convert YOLO detection results into structured JSON.
- Calculate worker count, PPE violations, and compliance score.
- Connect the YOLO inference pipeline with the FastAPI backend.
- Automatically store inspection records in the database.
- Validate inspection and prediction APIs.

### Deliverable
An integrated system where live detection results are automatically stored in the backend database.

---

## Week 3 – Dashboard & End-to-End Integration

### Objective
Complete the full AeroInspect AI workflow.

### Tasks
- Develop a dashboard displaying:
  - Total inspections
  - Worker count
  - Helmet violations
  - Vest violations
  - Compliance score
- Display inspection history from the database.
- Optimize detection and backend performance.
- Perform end-to-end integration testing.

### Deliverable
A complete workflow from live camera → YOLO detection → FastAPI backend → Database → Dashboard.

---

## Week 4 – Testing & Final Demonstration

### Objective
Finalize and validate the MVP.

### Tasks
- Perform end-to-end system testing.
- Fix bugs and improve performance.
- Validate detection accuracy using multiple construction site videos.
- Prepare project documentation and final demonstration.
- Polish the overall product for presentation.

### Deliverable
A working MVP capable of performing real-time PPE detection from a live video stream, automatically storing inspection records, and displaying construction safety analytics through the AeroInspect AI dashboard.
